{section|Build & Install}

Bracetax follows the {i|standard} OASIS setup (with OCamlbuild):
{code}
  ocaml setup.ml -configure  [--prefix /where/you/want]

  ocaml setup.ml -build

  ocaml setup.ml -install   (may require root privileges)
{end}

